:

1. *Morat* ću da se izvinem za svoje ponašanje. (I will have to apologize for my behavior.)
2. On *mora* da završi svoj zadatak danas. (He has to finish his task today.)
3. *Moraš* da budeš strpljiv. (You have to be patient.)
4. Ona je *morala* da ode. (She had to go.)
5. Ja *moram* da odem. (I have to go.)